a segment component score computer for computing segment component score for each of the segment components contained in each of the obtained segments, based on the distance between a position in which the received seed string appears in the segment and a position at which the segment component appears in the segment, and the segment scores computed for the segments; and,
a selector for selecting any of the segment components as candidates for instances contained in an expanded set that is an expansion of a set containing the received seed string, based on the computed segment component score for each of the obtained segment components.

